{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"立て続けに送られるものにかけて、","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-mur'salāti ʿur'fan ","translations":["By the ones sent forth","one after another","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-mur'salāti","ʿur'fan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1590],[2,1590,2565]]}},{"name":"77:2","price":"また、轟々という吹き荒れるものにかけて、","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-ʿāṣifāti ʿaṣfan ","translations":["And the winds that blow","violently","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-ʿāṣifāti","ʿaṣfan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2905]]}},{"name":"77:3","price":"また、広く拡散するもの¹にかけて、","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　何を「拡散する」かについては、「雲」「雨」「行いの帳簿（ちょうぼ）」などといった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：１５５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nāshirāti nashran ","translations":["And the ones that scatter","far and wide","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nāshirāti","nashran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2130],[2,2130,3365]]}},{"name":"77:4","price":"また、しっかりと分断するもの¹にかけて、","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「真理と虚妄（きょもう）を分断する啓示と共に下る天使*たち」「雲を分散させる風」といった解釈がある（前掲書、同頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-fāriqāti farqan ","translations":["And those who separate","(by the) Criterion","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-fāriqāti","farqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1600],[2,1600,2825]]}},{"name":"77:5","price":"また、教訓を投げかけるもの¹たちにかけて（誓う）。²","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　アッラー*から啓示を授かり、それを預言者*たちへと伝える天使*たちのこと（ムヤッサル５８０頁参照）。 ２　アーヤ*１－５で言及されている「誓い」については、整列者章１の訳注を参照。尚イブン・カスィール*によれば、これらの誓われているものについては、アーヤ*５を除き、それらが天使*のことを示しているか、あるいは風そのものであるかで、学者間の解釈の相違がある（８：２９７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mul'qiyāti dhik'ran ","translations":["And those who bring down","(the) Reminder","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mul'qiyāti","dhik'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2905]]}},{"name":"77:6","price":"弁解¹、あるいは警告ゆえに。","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　啓示によって、人々のアッラー*に対する弁解の余地はなくなる（ムヤッサル５８０頁参照）。関連するアーヤ*として、婦人章１６５、家畜章１３１、１５５－１５７、夜の旅章１５とその訳注、ター・ハー章１３４、詩人たち章２０８、創成者*章２４も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿudh'ran aw nudh'ran ","translations":["(As) justification","or","warning","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿudh'ran","aw","nudh'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,1190],[3,1190,2495]]}},{"name":"77:7","price":"あなた方に約束されていること¹は、確実に起こるのである。","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「約束されていること」とは、復活の日*と、そこでの清算や報いのこと（ムヤッサル５８０頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innamā tūʿadūna lawāqiʿun ","translations":["Indeed, what","you are promised","will surely occur","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["innamā","tūʿadūna","lawāqiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2800],[3,2800,4175]]}},{"name":"77:8","price":"星々（の光）が消された時、","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā al-nujūmu ṭumisat ","translations":["So when","the stars","are obliterated","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","al-nujūmu","ṭumisat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,2050],[3,2050,3185]]}},{"name":"77:9","price":"また、天が割れた時、","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-samāu furijat ","translations":["And when","the heaven","is cleft asunder","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-samāu","furijat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,2760],[3,2760,3645]]}},{"name":"77:10","price":"また、山々が粉々にされた時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*の天変地異の様子については洞窟章４７、ター・ハー章１０５－１０７、蟻章８８、山章９－１０、出来事章５－６、衣を纏（まと）う者章１４、階段章８－９、消息章２０、巻き込む章３、衝撃章４－５なども参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jibālu nusifat ","translations":["And when","the mountains","are blown away","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jibālu","nusifat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,1540],[3,1540,2685]]}},{"name":"77:11","price":"また、使徒*たちが（、その民との決着まで、）時間¹を定められた時、","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　これは、使徒*たちが自分たちの民について証言する、復活の日*のこと（アル＝バガウィー５：１９６参照）。婦人章４１とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-rusulu uqqitat ","translations":["And when","the Messengers","are gathered to their appointed time","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-rusulu","uqqitat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1450],[3,1450,2635]]}},{"name":"77:12","price":"（彼らには、こう言われる。）「一体、いずれの（偉大なる）日まで、（使徒*たちは）延期されたのか？","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"li-ayyi yawmin ujjilat ","translations":["For what","Day","are (these) postponed","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["li-ayyi","yawmin","ujjilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1630],[3,1630,2805]]}},{"name":"77:13","price":"裁決の日¹まで、である」。","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「裁決の日」については、整列者章２１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"liyawmi al-faṣli ","translations":["For (the) Day","(of) Judgment","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["liyawmi","al-faṣli",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1685]]}},{"name":"77:14","price":"（人間よ、）裁決の日が何かを、あなたに知らせるのは何か？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā yawmu al-faṣli ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","(is the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","yawmu","al-faṣli",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,2820],[3,2820,3170],[4,3170,3780],[5,3780,4875]]}},{"name":"77:15","price":"その日、（復活の日*を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1410],[3,1410,2420],[4,2420,5855]]}},{"name":"77:16","price":"われら*は、（自分たちの使徒*を噓つき呼ばわりしたことゆえ、）昔の人々を滅ぼしたのではなかったか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nuh'liki al-awalīna ","translations":["Did not","We destroy","the former (people)","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nuh'liki","al-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,550],[2,550,1370],[3,1370,4525]]}},{"name":"77:17","price":"それから、われら*は（彼らと同様であった）後代の者たちを、彼らに続かせるのだ。","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma nut'biʿuhumu al-ākhirīna ","translations":["Then","We follow them up","(with) the later ones","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","nut'biʿuhumu","al-ākhirīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,2290],[3,2290,5325]]}},{"name":"77:18","price":"そのように、われら*は（使徒*ムハンマド*を噓つき呼ばわりした）罪悪者たちに対して、するのである。","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kadhālika nafʿalu bil-muj'rimīna ","translations":["Thus","We deal","with the criminals","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["kadhālika","nafʿalu","bil-muj'rimīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1820],[3,1820,5145]]}},{"name":"77:19","price":"（復活の）その日、（アッラーの唯一性*と、使徒*と、復活と報いを）嘘呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1400],[2,1400,2460],[3,2460,6085]]}},{"name":"77:20","price":"（不信仰者*たちよ、）われら*はあなた方を、卑しい液体¹から創ったのではないか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「卑しい液体」については、アッ＝サジダ*章８の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nakhluqkkum min māin mahīnin ","translations":["Did not","We create you","from","a water","despicable","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nakhluqkkum","min","māin","mahīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1940],[3,1940,2680],[4,2680,5670],[5,5670,8675]]}},{"name":"77:21","price":"そしてそれを、しっかりとした定着場¹に設えたのでは？","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「しっかりとした定着場」については、信仰者たち章１３の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fajaʿalnāhu fī qarārin makīnin ","translations":["Then We placed it","in","an abode","safe","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fajaʿalnāhu","fī","qarārin","makīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,1690],[3,1690,2510],[4,2510,5605]]}},{"name":"77:22","price":"定められた階段¹まで。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまり、出産の時期のこと（アル＝バガウィー５：１９７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ilā qadarin maʿlūmin ","translations":["For","a period","known","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["ilā","qadarin","maʿlūmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,520],[2,520,1130],[3,1130,5005]]}},{"name":"77:23","price":"われら*は、（その創造、造形、出産を）調整したのだ。調整するお方の何と素晴らしいことか。","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"faqadarnā faniʿ'ma al-qādirūna ","translations":["So We measured","and Best","(are We to) measure","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["faqadarnā","faniʿ'ma","al-qādirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1830],[3,1830,4835]]}},{"name":"77:24","price":"（復活の）その日、（われら*の力を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,2410],[3,2410,5545]]}},{"name":"77:25","price":"われら*は大地を、収容するものとしたのではないか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam najʿali al-arḍa kifātan ","translations":["Have not","We made","the earth","a receptacle","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","najʿali","al-arḍa","kifātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,1310],[3,1310,2040],[4,2040,3275]]}},{"name":"77:26","price":"（数えきれないほどの）生者たちと死者たちを（、収容するものと）？","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"aḥyāan wa-amwātan ","translations":["(For the) living","and (the) dead","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["aḥyāan","wa-amwātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3240],[2,3240,5025]]}},{"name":"77:27","price":"また、われら*はそこ（大地）に、高く聳える堅固な山々を置き、あなた方に美味なる水を飲ませてやった。","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿalnā fīhā rawāsiya shāmikhātin wa-asqaynākum māan furātan ","translations":["And We made","therein","firmly set mountains","lofty","and We gave you to drink","water ","sweet","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿalnā","fīhā","rawāsiya","shāmikhātin","wa-asqaynākum","māan","furātan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,1950],[3,1950,2920],[4,2920,4760],[5,4760,6370],[6,6370,9720],[7,9720,11365]]}},{"name":"77:28","price":"（復活の）その日、（これらの恩恵を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2410],[3,2410,5915]]}},{"name":"77:29","price":"（復活の日*、不信仰者*たちには、こう言われる。）「（現世で）あなた方が噓呼ばわりしていたもの（地獄の懲罰）へと、進み行くがよい。","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inṭaliqū ilā mā kuntum bihi tukadhibūna ","translations":["Proceed","to","what","you used to","in it","deny","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["inṭaliqū","ilā","mā","kuntum","bihi","tukadhibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3780],[2,3780,4350],[3,4350,4680],[4,4680,7070],[5,7070,7590],[6,7590,11115]]}},{"name":"77:30","price":"三つ又の¹（煙の）陰へと、進み行け」。","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　燃え立つ炎と共に上る煙が、その激しさゆえに三本に分かれる様子とされる（イブン・カスィール８：２９９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inṭaliqū ilā ẓillin dhī thalāthi shuʿabin ","translations":["Proceed","to","a shadow","having","three","columns","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["inṭaliqū","ilā","ẓillin","dhī","thalāthi","shuʿabin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3779],[2,3779,4329],[3,4329,5939],[4,5939,6299],[5,6299,7129],[6,7129,7854]]}},{"name":"77:31","price":"濃影でもなく、炎から防いでもくれない（陰へ）。","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā ẓalīlin walā yugh'nī mina al-lahabi ","translations":["No","cool shade","and not","availing","against","the flame","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","ẓalīlin","walā","yugh'nī","mina","al-lahabi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,2120],[3,2120,2660],[4,2660,3510],[5,3510,3810],[6,3810,5065]]}},{"name":"77:32","price":"実にそれ（地獄）は、城のような（巨大な）火花を飛ばす。","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahā tarmī bishararin kal-qaṣri ","translations":["Indeed, it","throws up","sparks","as the fortress","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["innahā","tarmī","bishararin","kal-qaṣri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1700],[2,1700,2440],[3,2440,3970],[4,3970,5255]]}},{"name":"77:33","price":"まるで、黄褐色のラクダの一群¹のような（火花を）。","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　その大きさ、色、炎から飛び散って遠ざかっていく動きが、黄褐色のラクダの一群に例えられているのだという（イブン・アーシュール２９：４３７参照）。また、黄褐色ではなく黒色という説もある（イブン・カスィール８：２９９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ka-annahu jimālatun ṣuf'run ","translations":["As if they (were)","camels","yellow","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["ka-annahu","jimālatun","ṣuf'run",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,3850],[3,3850,4795]]}},{"name":"77:34","price":"（復活の）その日、（アッラー*の警告を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,2330],[3,2330,6485]]}},{"name":"77:35","price":"これは、彼ら（噓呼ばわりしていた者たちが、自分たちを益することを）喋ることがない¹（復活の）日*。","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　復活の日、「喋ることがない」ことについては、夜の旅章９７の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"hādhā yawmu lā yanṭiqūna ","translations":["This","(is) a Day","not","they will speak","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["hādhā","yawmu","lā","yanṭiqūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,1440],[3,1440,2000],[4,2000,5615]]}},{"name":"77:36","price":"また、彼らに（弁明が）許可されることで、言い訳することもない（日）。","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yu'dhanu lahum fayaʿtadhirūna ","translations":["And not","will it be permitted","for them","to make excuses","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yu'dhanu","lahum","fayaʿtadhirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1410],[3,1410,1970],[4,1970,5485]]}},{"name":"77:37","price":"（復活の）その日、（この日の出来事を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2500],[3,2500,6445]]}},{"name":"77:38","price":"これは裁決の日¹。われら*はあなた方（不信仰者*たち）と、昔の（不信仰だった）人々を集結させた。","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「裁決の日」については、整列者章２１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"hādhā yawmu al-faṣli jamaʿnākum wal-awalīna ","translations":["This","(is the) Day","(of) Judgment","We have gathered you","and the former (people)","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["hādhā","yawmu","al-faṣli","jamaʿnākum","wal-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,1470],[3,1470,2290],[4,2290,3690],[5,3690,7075]]}},{"name":"77:39","price":"それで、もしあなた方に（懲罰から逃れる）策略があるのなら、われら*に策略してみよ。","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-in kāna lakum kaydun fakīdūni ","translations":["So if","is","for you","a plan","then plan against Me","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-in","kāna","lakum","kaydun","fakīdūni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,2010],[3,2010,2650],[4,2650,4170],[5,4170,7175]]}},{"name":"77:40","price":"（復活の）その日、（復活の日*を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,2380],[3,2380,6325]]}},{"name":"77:41","price":"本当に敬虔な*者たちは、（その日、木々の）陰と泉のもとにある。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-mutaqīna fī ẓilālin waʿuyūnin ","translations":["Indeed","the righteous","(will be) in","shades","and springs","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-mutaqīna","fī","ẓilālin","waʿuyūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,2770],[3,2770,3130],[4,3130,4869],[5,4869,8034]]}},{"name":"77:42","price":"また、自分たちが欲する果実のもとに。","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wafawākiha mimmā yashtahūna ","translations":["And fruits","from what","they desire","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["wafawākiha","mimmā","yashtahūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,2750],[3,2750,6025]]}},{"name":"77:43","price":"（彼らには、こう言われる。）「自分たちが（現世で）行っていた（正しい）こと（の報い）ゆえに、おいしく食べ、飲むのだ。¹","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　天国の民の飲食物については、ヤー・スィーン章５７、整列者章４５－４７、サード章５１、詳細にされた章３１、金の装飾章７３、煙霧章５５、ムハンマド*章１５、山章２２、慈悲あまねき*お方章５２、６８、出来事章１７－２１、真実章２３、人間章５－６、１４、１７－１８、２１、消息章３４、量を減らす者たち章２５－２８も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kulū wa-ish'rabū hanīan bimā kuntum taʿmalūna ","translations":["Eat","and drink","(in) satisfaction","for what","you used to","do","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["kulū","wa-ish'rabū","hanīan","bimā","kuntum","taʿmalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1490],[3,1490,4689],[4,4689,5279],[5,5279,6819],[6,6819,9484]]}},{"name":"77:44","price":"本当に、われら*はこのように、善を尽くす者¹たちに報いるのだから」。","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「善を尽くす者」については、蜜蜂章１２８の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innā kadhālika najzī al-muḥ'sinīna ","translations":["Indeed, We","thus","reward","the good-doers","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","kadhālika","najzī","al-muḥ'sinīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,2340],[3,2340,2900],[4,2900,5715]]}},{"name":"77:45","price":"（復活の）その日、（報いと清算を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(45)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2580],[3,2580,6385]]}},{"name":"77:46","price":"（不信仰者*たちよ、）僅かな間、食べ、楽しむがよい。本当にあなた方は、（シルク*という罪を犯す）罪悪者なのだ。","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kulū watamattaʿū qalīlan innakum muj'rimūna ","translations":["Eat","and enjoy yourselves","a little","indeed, you","(are) criminals","(46)"],"transliterationArr":["kulū","watamattaʿū","qalīlan","innakum","muj'rimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1890],[3,1890,2810],[4,2810,4420],[5,4420,7985]]}},{"name":"77:47","price":"（復活の）その日、（清算と報いの日を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(47)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2160],[3,2160,6225]]}},{"name":"77:48","price":"彼ら（シルク*の徒）は、自分たちに「ルクーゥ*せよ」と言われても、ルクーゥ*しない。¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまり、礼拝せよ、と言われてもしないということ（ムヤッサル５８１頁参照）。 一説には、これは復活の日*のこと（アル＝バガウィー５：１９８－１９９参照）。筆章４２－４３とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā qīla lahumu ir'kaʿū lā yarkaʿūna ","translations":["And when","it is said","to them","Bow","not","they bow","(48)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","qīla","lahumu","ir'kaʿū","lā","yarkaʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1470],[3,1470,2060],[4,2060,2850],[5,2850,3230],[6,3230,6445]]}},{"name":"77:49","price":"（復活の）その日、（アッラー*の御徴を）噓呼ばわりしていた者たちに、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(49)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1770],[2,1770,2640],[3,2640,6705]]}},{"name":"77:50","price":"ならば一体、彼らはそれ（クルアーン*）を差しおいて、いかなる話を信じるというのか？","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ḥadīthin baʿdahu yu'minūna ","translations":["Then in what","statement","after it","will they believe","(50)"],"transl